 896:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | i.e. default value is 0.
 897:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 898:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | Sine of the minimum tilt angle in portrait down
 899:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | direction of the device when wrist is rolled away
 900:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | (roll-out) from user.
