 904:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 905:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | Value of minimum time difference between wrist
 906:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | roll-out and roll-in movement during flick gesture.
 907:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *  min_flick_samples       | Range is 3 to 5 samples at 50Hz (i.e. 0.06 to 0.1 seconds).
