 909:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 910:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | Maximum time within which gesture movement has to be completed.
 911:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *  max_duration            | Range is 150 to 250 samples at 50Hz (i.e. 3 to 5 seconds).
 912:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | Default value is 200 (i.e. 4 seconds).
 913:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
