1077:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * @brief This internal API gets wrist gesture configurations like wearable-arm,
1078:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * and output-configuration.
1079:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *
1080:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * @param[out]      config    : Structure instance of bmi2_wrist_gest_config.
1081:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * @param[in, out]  dev       : Structure instance of bmi2_dev.
1082:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *
1083:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * @verbatim
1084:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1085:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *  bmi2_wrist_gest_config  |
1086:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *  Structure parameters    |               Description
1087:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1088:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | Device in left (0) or right (1) arm. By default,
1089:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *  wearable_arm            | the wearable device is assumed to be in left arm
1090:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | i.e. default value is 0.
1091:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1092:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | Sine of the minimum tilt angle in portrait down
1093:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | direction of the device when wrist is rolled away
1094:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | (roll-out) from user.
1095:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *  min_flick_peak          | The configuration parameter is scaled by 2048
1096:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | i.e. 2048 * sin(angle).
1097:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | Range is 1448 to 1774. Default value is 1774.
1098:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1099:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | Value of minimum time difference between wrist
1100:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | roll-out and roll-in movement during flick gesture.
1101:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *  min_flick_samples       | Range is 3 to 5 samples at 50Hz (i.e. 0.06 to 0.1 seconds).
1102:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | Default value is 4 (i.e. 0.08 seconds).
1103:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1104:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | Maximum time within which gesture movement has to be completed.
1105:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *  max_duration            | Range is 150 to 250 samples at 50Hz (i.e. 3 to 5 seconds).
1106:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *                          | Default value is 200 (i.e. 4 seconds).
1107:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1108:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * @endverbatim
1109:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  *
1110:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * @return Result of API execution status
1111:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * @retval 0 -> Success
1112:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  * @retval < 0 -> Fail
1113:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi270.c ****  */
